name: Shivers Garden Bar & Restaurant Goa

reviews.review_text: We love the staff and food at this restaurant. We visited it 3 times whilst on a 14 day trip to Goa. I cannot describe how fabulous the food is. A wide assortment of dishes to choose from but a nice break away from curry. It is situated only 100 metres down a side street next to the Holiday Inn on the main road. It's not far to walk, off the main track, for a terrific experience. Well done team you made our holiday feel very special.

I went with my family to have lobster and other food variety. Ordered Lobster which was nicely cooked with right amount of spices as told to server. We also had their burnt garlic noodles which were good too.

They also offered welcome drink prepared from Kumkum which was good in taste.

Also drinks which we ordered were nice and refreshing. They also have 4 rooms which people can take on rent, property is near to a beach.

Overall, good Experience.

This was indeed a good experience dinning at this restaurant. Service was amazing.
Deepanshu and lolo were very friendly and amazed us with their services.
Food and ambience both were outstanding.
Tried complimentary paan which was grown in their own garden, that was something which we tried for the first time and seriously, what an experience it was.
Overall 10/10.

description:
**Shivers Garden Bar & Restaurant: A Hidden Gem in Goa**

Nestled just a stone's throw away from the bustling main road and only 100 meters from the Holiday Inn, Shivers Garden Bar & Restaurant has successfully carved a niche for itself, securing an impressive rating of 4.6 from 2,294 guests. This charming establishment offers a delightful escape from the ordinary, serving a range of favorite dishes that have visitors raving. With tags frequently appearing in reviews such as “thali,” “Goan,” “romantic,” and “paan,” it’s clear that Shivers has mastered both local flavors and unique dining experiences.

**Ambiance & Design**

At Shivers, guests can expect an inviting and serene atmosphere enhanced by lush greenery and tasteful décor. The photos depict a cozy outdoor seating area surrounded by vibrant gardens, perfect for a romantic evening under the stars or a relaxed afternoon with family. Dim lighting complements the natural beauty, creating an intimate setting that welcomes guests into a tranquil retreat away from the bustling beach crowd. Reviewers have noted the subtle background music that enhances the dining experience without overpowering conversations, making it a truly enchanting venue.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Shivers is a celebration of Goan flavors with an impressive variety of dishes. Signature offerings include their renowned lobster, which guests commend for its perfect seasoning and preparation. One family delighted in this very dish, praising the balance of spices and the skillful cooking that elevates the seafood experience. Additionally, the burnt garlic noodles have received accolades for their flavor, proving to be excellent companions to the seafood options.

A standout experience mentioned by diners was the complimentary paan, harvested from the restaurant's own garden. This delightful treat left one guest describing it as “an experience worth trying for the first time.” The restaurant also caters to diverse dietary preferences, ensuring there’s something for everyone, whether you are seeking a traditional thali or regional seafood delights.

**Customer Experience & Service**

The level of service at Shivers is frequently highlighted in glowing reviews. Staff members like Deepanshu and Lolo were described as extraordinarily friendly and attentive, enriching the dining experience and creating a welcoming environment. Reviewers consistently note the quick turnaround on orders, and the creativity with welcome drinks—like the refreshing kumkum beverage—signifies a thoughtful touch that enhances the overall customer experience. With options for reservations and nearby accommodations, Shivers ensures that both walk-in patrons and those planning a visit will feel well taken care of.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Shivers Garden Bar & Restaurant has received overwhelming positive sentiment among its patrons, often described as a delightful and memorable experience. With many guests returning multiple times during their visits to Goa, it’s evident this establishment leaves a significant mark. The buzz surrounding it on social media and review platforms further emphasizes its popularity, with customers sharing their experiences and stunning food photography that showcases the restaurant's culinary artistry.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Images from customer visits highlight the lush greenery enveloping the restaurant, complemented by intimate tables adorned with beautiful dish presentations. The photos capture vibrant plates of seafood and other local delicacies, with reviews echoing the stunning presentation and delicious tastes of the meals. This visual testimony of joy paired with the delightful dishes reflects the restaurant's commitment to quality and guest satisfaction.

In summary, Shivers Garden Bar & Restaurant not only highlights the rich culinary traditions of Goa but also serves as an oasis of relaxation and warmth. This charming venue is undoubtedly a must-visit for anyone looking to indulge in authentic flavors while enjoying a delightful and romantic ambiance. With its commendable service and exquisite menu, it promises a dining experience that will linger in your memory long after you’ve left its enchanting garden.
